name: CloudFrontForwardedValuesCookies
description: Cookies is a property of the CloudFront ForwardedValues that describes which cookies are forwarded to the Amazon CloudFront origin.

properties.name: Forward
properties.description: The cookies to forward to the origin of the cache behavior. You can specify none, all, or whitelist.

properties.name: WhitelistedNames
properties.description: The names of cookies to forward to the origin for the cache behavior.
